Package: EZ2
Type: Package
Title: Modeling Human Response Times and Accuracy using the EZ/EZ2 Diffusion Model
Version: 1.2.0
Author: Raoul Grasman
Maintainer: Raoul Grasman <rgrasman@uva.nl>
Description: Fitting simplified versions of Ratcliff's (1978) diffusion model (the EZ and EZ2 models) for human and monkey response times and accuracy to the means and variances of the observables. 
License: GPL-2
